Description: Branching process simulation model of infectious disease
    transmission with flexible parameterisation of epidemiology and targeted
    interventions, including isolation, contact tracing and quarantine, to
    reduce transmission, together with functions to evaluate outbreak control.
    Introduced in Hellewell et al. (2020) <doi:10.1016/S2214-109X(20)30074-7>.
